113 exceeding five years.
114 (j) This section shall not apply to any of the
115 following:
116 (1) Lawful hunting, fishing, and trapping.
117 (2) Generally accepted animal husbandry, agricultural,
118 and wildlife management practices.
119 (3) The practice of veterinary medicine.
120 (4) Pest control.
121 (5) Research that complies with applicable federal and
122 state laws.
123 (k) This section is in addition to, and not a
124 substitute for, the crimes provided by Sections 13A-11-14,
125 13A-11-14.1, and 13A-11-241, Code of Alabama 1975.
126 Section 2. This act shall become effective on October
127 1, 2026.
